<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-2391] ExpandoMetaClass: Unable to override DGM asType method on certain types</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2391</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/EMC-Problem-in-Groovy-1.5---Overriding-%22asType%22-method-on-ArrayList-td14298090.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/EMC-Problem-in-Groovy-1.5---Overriding-%22asType%22-method-on-ArrayList-td14298090.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve just stumbled upon a problem with Groovy 1.5 which was already solved in some previous betas... It&apos;s about overriding the asType method on the ArrayList.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Doing something like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ArrayList.metaClass.asType = &lt;/p&gt;
{ Class clazz -&amp;gt; /* .... */ }
&lt;p&gt;ArrayList.metaClass.initialize()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;then&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1,2,3&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; as /* any class here */&lt;br/&gt;
or&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1,2,3&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.asType( /* any class here */)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;does not invoke the closure code...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Using emc stuff and asType method with other classes works so far as I can say....&lt;/p&gt;</description>
